dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2019. [Description and X,Y location data for monumented Adams County PLSS Section Corners.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Custodial data for Adams County PLSS corner monuments, by type and location, including tie sheet links.]
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Adams County Register of Deeds. [Adams County GIS.]
